{"title":"CentOS8 安装 pyenv 进行Python版本管理","uid":"799caa19913ca1b7943f59953e293be8","slug":"centos8-install-pyenv","date":"2023-01-10T16:37:05.000Z","updated":"2023-01-10T16:37:05.000Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/centos8-install-pyenv.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1484417894907-623942c8ee29","content":"<h2 id=\"安装-pyenv\"><a href=\"#安装-pyenv\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"安装  pyenv\"></a>安装  <em><a href=\"https://github.com/pyenv/pyenv\"><code>pyenv</code></a></em></h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token function\">curl</span> https://pyenv.run <span class=\"token operator\">|</span> <span class=\"token function\">bash</span><span aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"line-numbers-rows\"><span></span></span></code></pre>\n<h2 id=\"pyenv-基本命令\"><a href=\"#pyenv-基本命令\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"pyenv 基本命令\"></a><em><a href=\"https://github.com/pyenv/pyenv\"><code>pyenv</code></a></em> 基本命令</h2><pre class=\"line-numbers language-bash\" data-language=\"bash\"><code class=\"language-bash\"><span class=\"token comment\"># 查看pyenv命令</span>\npyenv commands\n<span class=\"token comment\"># 查看可安装的python版本</span>\npyenv <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">--list</span> \n<span class=\"token comment\"># 查看已安装版本</span>\npyenv versions \n<span class=\"token comment\"># 查看当前使用的python版本</span>\npyenv version \n<span class=\"token comment\"># 安装python</span>\npyenv <span class=\"token function\">install</span> <span class=\"token parameter variable\">-v</span> 版本号 \n<span class=\"token comment\"># 刷新python已安装列表</span>\npyenv rehash \n<span class=\"token comment\"># 删除python</span>\npyenv uninstall 版本号 \n<span class=\"token comment\"># 设置当前全局python版本</span>\npyenv global 版本号 \n<span class=\"token comment\"># 设置局部python版本</span>\npyenv <span class=\"token builtin class-name\">local</span> 版本号 \n<span class=\"token commen